text: Magnoliopsida or dicotyledons is the name of a class of plants in taxonomy. They are also called dicots. It is the biggest group of flowering plants. Seedlings in this group have two seed leaves. Monocots have one seed leaf. ==Examples of the group== *Oaks *Sunflowers *Roses *Blackberries * Blueberry * Bilberry Category:Flowering plants tr:Çift çenekliler
title: Magnoliopsida
